'''''Prince of Lies''''', by [[James Lowder]], is the fourth book of the [[Avatar series]].
{{quote|''Revenge of a God.''

''The [[Time of Troubles]] is at an end, and the [[god]]s have been restored to their rightful places.''

''The soul of [[Kelemvor Lyonsbane]], former lover of the [[Midnight|goddess of magic]], remains hidden from the mad god [[Cyric]].''

''The will of one such as Cyric, when bent on revenge, is not so easily thwarted.''}}

